messages.messageBody:
I have 5kids (hence the name) and I just let them pick the food I buy
and let them eat it while we have it (when its gone its gone till the
next time I have the $$$ to go shopping again)
I don't limit at all and they go shopping with me or lett me know what
they like to eat so it works out pretty well. But they know I we are
not always going to have everything they like to eat.
One time when discribing going food shopping with me to one of the
kids friends they said just ask mom so she can say yes!


jean
